Dr.GuojiGuoisaprofessoratCenterforStemCellandRegenerativeMedicine,ZhejiangUniversitySchoolofMedicine.HewasbornatWuhanin1983.HeobtainedhisPh.DatNationalUniversityofSingaporein2005,andthenmovedtoHarvardMedicalSchoolforpostdoctraining.In2014,hewasrecuitedanddirectlytenuredatZhejiangUniversityunder&quot;HighLevelTalentRecruitmentProgram&quot;.HeisnowoneoftheyoungestprofessorsinZhejiangUniversity.In2015,hewasselectedforthe&quot;1000YouthTalentPlan&quot;ofChina.

Dr.GuojiGuo'slabisinterestedinmolecularmechanismsofstemcellself-renewal,aswellasoptimizationforstemcellinvitrocultureconditions.Hislabspecializesinadvancedbiotechnologies,suchassinglecellanalysis,CRISPR/Cas9genomeeditingandcombinatorialchemicalscreening.
			
				
